'''''Sumer''''' is a 1981 video game published by Crystal Computer for the [[Apple II]], [[Atari 8-bit computers]], [[Commodore PET]], and [[TRS-80]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mocagh.org/firstera/sandsofmars-manual.pdf|title=Sands of Mars manual|page=28}}</ref>

==Contents==
''Sumer'' is a game in which the player tries to establish a kingdom by managing it as it grows.<ref name="SG"/>

